070: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **主要故障模式**：所有frontend实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）都报告相同的连接错误\n2. **目标服务**：cartservice（IP: 10.233.46.196, 端口: 7070）\n3. **错误类型**：端口连接拒绝（connection refused）\n4. **影响范围**：购物车相关功能完全失效（添加商品、查看购物车、结账）\n\n**建议下一步**：需要进一步检查cartservice的健康状态、端口配置和网络连接情况，以确定是cartservice本身故障还是网络配置问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple frontend pods (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2) show high error_ratio and server_error_ratio during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio and server_error_ratio increased significantly for frontend pods.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"productcatalogservice-1 and productcatalogservice-2 show high client_error_ratio and error_ratio.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio and error_ratio spiked for these pods.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice-0 and shippingservice-1 exhibit high error_ratio and client_error_ratio.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio and client_error_ratio increased significantly.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice pods (cartservice-0, cartservice-1, cartservice-2) show high rrt and rrt_max values.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt and rrt_max values increased significantly, indicating latency issues.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"redis-cart-0 shows high rrt_max and pod_cpu_usage changes.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max and pod_cpu_usage metrics indicate potential performance issues.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于对系统故障期间（2025-06-11T00:10:20Z 至 2025-06-11T00:28:20Z）的调用链数据分析，我发现了显著的异常模式。以下是详细的根因分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"productcatalogservice->tidb\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService出现大量连接拒绝错误（connection refused），所有frontend节点和checkoutservice节点都无法连接到10.233.46.196:7070，这是最下游的根因服务\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService的PlaceOrder操作出现大量错误（状态码13），错误信息显示是由于CartService不可用导致的级联故障\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend服务出现大量HTTP 500错误，这是由下游CartService和CheckoutService故障引起的受害者服务\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService的GetProduct操作延迟显著增加，从正常约10-11ms增加到12-14ms，延迟倍数约1.2-1.4倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **主要根因**：**CartService完全不可用**，表现为连接拒绝错误（connection refused），这是系统故障的根本原因。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - CartService故障 → CheckoutService无法获取购物车 → Frontend服务返回500错误\n\n3. **延迟异常**：\n   - CheckoutService的PlaceOrder操作延迟显著下降（从150ms降至5-9ms），这是Fast Fail模式，表明请求被快速拒绝\n   - ProductCatalogService有轻微延迟增加，但影响相对较小\n\n4. **影响范围**：所有frontend节点和checkoutservice节点都受到影响，故障具有全局性。\n\n建议优先检查CartService的运行状态和网络连接配置。"}
